    <id>starrate</id>
    <name>StarRate</name>
    <summary>Professional photo rating and culling tool for photographers</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
StarRate is a professional photo rating and culling tool for photographers, seamlessly integrated into Nextcloud.

**Features:**
- Full-screen gallery with grid and loupe view (like Adobe Lightroom)
- Star ratings (0–5) and color labels (Red/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple)
- Ratings written directly into JPEG/XMP metadata
- Batch rating with multi-selection (Shift+click, Ctrl+click)
- Guest share links for models and clients (no Nextcloud login required)
- Keyboard shortcuts like Lightroom (0–5 stars, 6–9 colors, P/X for pick/reject)
- Smooth zoom up to 400%, pan and pinch-to-zoom on mobile
- Filter by stars and colors, combinable
- Dark, professional UI theme optimized for photo work
    ]]></description>

